sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant CLI as manage_tool_inventory.py
    participant JSON as tool_inventory.json
    participant Distiller as distiller.py
    participant LLM as Granite Model
    participant Cache as rlm_tool_cache.json

    note over CLI, Cache: 1. Forward Flow (Trigger)
    User->>CLI: add tool (path)
    CLI->>JSON: Create entry
    CLI->>Distiller: _distill_tool(path)
    
    note over Distiller, Cache: 2. Analysis & Caching
    Distiller->>LLM: Summarize(code)
    LLM-->>Distiller: JSON { purpose, ... }
    Distiller->>Cache: Save RLM Entry
    
    note over Distiller, CLI: 3. Feedback Loop (Enrichment)
    Distiller->>CLI: update_tool(path, purpose, suppress=True)
    
    note over CLI, JSON: 4. Final Updates (Suppressed)
    CLI->>JSON: Update Description

